    "headline": "The Trade Desk (NASDAQ:TTD) Posts Better-Than-Expected Sales In Q1 CY2026 But Stock Drops 15%",
    "summary": "Digital advertising platform The Trade Desk (NASDAQ:TTD) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q1 CY2026, with sales up 11.8% year on year to $688.9 million. On the other hand, next quarter’s revenue guidance of $750 million was less impressive, coming in 2.9% below analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.28 per share was 12.4% below analysts’ consensus estimates.",
